flowchart LR
  A[Source documents] --> B[Chunks + metadata]
  B --> C[Embeddings]
  C --> D[(Staging vector index)]
  D --> E[Retrieval eval gate]
  E --> F[(Production index)]
  G[User query] --> H[Query embedding]
  H --> I[Filters + vector search]
  F --> I
  I --> J[Context + citations]
  E --> K[Rollback / keep old index]
